---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
const today = new Date();
const lastUpdated = `${today.getFullYear()}-${String(today.getMonth() + 1).padStart(2, "0")}-${String(today.getDate()).padStart(2, "0")}`;
---

<Layout title="Terms & Conditions">
  <main class="min-h-screen bg-base-200">
    <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 py-12">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-2">Light Lane Terms &amp; Conditions</h1>
      <p class="text-sm opacity-70 mb-8">
        Last Updated: {lastUpdated} • Contact: <a
          href="mailto:support@lightlane.app"
          class="link link-primary">support@lightlane.app</a
        >
      </p>

      <ol class="space-y-10 list-decimal list-inside">
        <li id="acceptance" class="space-y-4">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">Acceptance of Terms</h2>
          <p>
            By accessing, installing, downloading, or using Light Lane
            ("Software," "Application," "App," "We," "Us," or "Our"), you agree
            to be bound by these Terms &amp; Conditions ("Terms"). If you do not
            agree, you must immediately discontinue all use and uninstall the
            Software.
          </p>
          <p>
            These Terms apply to all users, whether authorized, invited, or
            otherwise. Any unauthorized use is strictly prohibited and may
            result in legal action.
          </p>
        </li>
        <li id="beta" class="space-y-4">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">Early Beta &amp; Launch</h2>
          <p>
            Light Lane is publicly available and in early beta. Features may
            evolve and stability may vary as we iterate. We’ll provide support
            and timely fixes to ensure a reliable experience.
          </p>
          <p>
            After purchasing, downloads are delivered by email. Setup assistance
            is available to help you get running quickly.
          </p>
        </li>
        <li id="refunds" class="space-y-4">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">No Refund Policy</h2>
          <p><strong>All payments are final.</strong></p>
          <p>
            We do not offer refunds under any circumstances, including but not
            limited to dissatisfaction, compatibility issues, feature requests,
            or changes in your business needs. By purchasing or subscribing, you
            acknowledge and accept this strict no-refund policy.
          </p>
        </li>
        <li id="license" class="space-y-4">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">
            License Grant &amp; Restrictions
          </h2>
          <p>
            We grant you a limited, non-exclusive, non-transferable, revocable
            license to install and use Light Lane for the purpose intended
            during the beta period.
          </p>
          <p class="font-medium">You agree NOT to:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-4">
            <li>
              Copy, modify, reverse-engineer, decompile, disassemble, or create
              derivative works of the Software.
            </li>
            <li>Share, sell, lease, rent, or sublicense your access.</li>
            <li>Attempt to bypass invitation-only restrictions.</li>
            <li>
              Use the Software for illegal purposes or in violation of any laws.
            </li>
          </ul>
          <p>
            Any violation of these terms will result in immediate termination of
            your license and potential legal action.
          </p>
        </li>
        <li id="ip" class="space-y-4">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">Intellectual Property</h2>
          <p>
            All intellectual property rights in Light Lane, including but not
            limited to software code, trademarks, trade secrets, and designs,
            remain the exclusive property of Light Lane and its licensors.
          </p>
          <p>You do not acquire any ownership rights by using the Software.</p>
        </li>
        <li id="beta-risks" class="space-y-4">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">Beta Features &amp; Risks</h2>
          <p>You understand that Light Lane is in beta testing, which means:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-4">
            <li>
              The Software may contain bugs, errors, or incomplete features.
            </li>
            <li>Features may change or be removed without notice.</li>
            <li>There may be downtime or unexpected behavior.</li>
          </ul>
          <p>
            By participating in the beta, you accept these risks and agree that
            we are not liable for any loss, damage, or inconvenience resulting
            from the use of the Software.
          </p>
        </li>
        <li id="liability" class="space-y-4">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">Limitation of Liability</h2>
          <p>
            To the maximum extent permitted by law, Light Lane and its
            affiliates shall not be liable for any indirect, incidental,
            special, consequential, or punitive damages, including loss of
            profits, business interruption, or loss of data, arising from your
            use of the Software.
          </p>
          <p>
            In all cases, our total liability will be limited to the amount you
            paid for the Software.
          </p>
        </li>
        <li id="termination" class="space-y-4">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">Termination</h2>
          <p>
            We reserve the right to suspend or terminate your access without
            notice if you violate these Terms or engage in any unauthorized or
            harmful activity. Upon termination, you must immediately uninstall
            and cease all use of the Software.
          </p>
        </li>
        <li id="law" class="space-y-4">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">
            Governing Law &amp; Jurisdiction
          </h2>
          <p>
            These Terms shall be governed by and construed in accordance with
            the laws of New Zealand, without regard to its conflict of law
            principles. Any disputes shall be subject to the exclusive
            jurisdiction of the courts located in Nelson, New Zealand.
          </p>
        </li>
        <li id="changes" class="space-y-4">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">Changes to Terms</h2>
          <p>
            We may update these Terms at any time. Continued use of the Software
            after changes are posted constitutes your acceptance of the updated
            Terms.
          </p>
        </li>
        <li id="contact" class="space-y-4">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">Contact</h2>
          <p>
            For any questions or concerns regarding these Terms, please contact: <a
              href="mailto:support@lightlane.app"
              class="link">support@lightlane.app</a
            >
          </p>
        </li>
      </ol>
    </section>
  </main>
</Layout>
